Auth Interface Context Refactoring

This plan aligns the `AuthService` interface with the concrete `Service` struct, ensuring `context.Context` is properly propagated throughout the authentication domain for cancellation, timeouts, and tracing.

## Objectives
- Plumb `context.Context` through all `Service` methods in `backend/internal/auth/service.go`.
- Ensure `Service` actually satisfies the `AuthService` interface, or rewrite the interface to match reality.
- Replace or remove hardcoded stub token implementations (`CreatePasswordResetToken`, etc.).

## Scope
- `backend/internal/auth/interface.go`
- `backend/internal/auth/service.go`
- Callers of `AuthService` in `handlers.go` and `mfarequired.go`
